{"tid":2415443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撰報告小組 林鄭心腹領軍","createTime":"2021-02-20T08:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T09:20:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad8a2bc079f89b6192fc3bf11e991b9ef2d9eb5","tid":2415443,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/ROWMP4SFAZBKBFK2D37JZYY6BY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FROWMP4SFAZBKBFK2D37JZYY6BY%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkhVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=e8172f51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FROWMP4SFAZBKBFK2D37JZYY6BY%2F&h=276d8042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/ROWMP4SFAZBKBFK2D37JZYY6BY/</a><br />\n<br />\n撰報告小組 林鄭心腹領軍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kwwSNz1p3ik_kngqV2F7SpE9B-w=/907x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LCLV4TQEK5CC5I4QX4YHVNIXKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkwwSNz1p3ik_kngqV2F7SpE9B-w%3D%2F907x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLCLV4TQEK5CC5I4QX4YHVNIXKI.jpg&h=2943aa16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丁葉燕薇<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】撰寫檢討報告的專責小組炮轟香港電台現時制度和管理欠缺透明度，編輯人員問責意識薄弱。然而這個小組本身也是透明度極低、源頭不明的神秘組織。由始至終政府僅公開兩名小組成員的身份，包括小組主任、特首林鄭月娥的愛將丁葉燕薇（圖），以及港台助理廣播處長張健華，長達92頁的檢討報告未有公開小組名單。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：梁家榮任內風波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商經局拒公開成員名單<br />\n<br />\n港台節目《頭條新聞》去年被裁定污衊和侮辱警方等投訴成立，商經局同年5月宣佈成立專責小組檢討港台，但至7月才公佈小組由丁葉燕薇掌舵。<span class=\"orange\">局方公佈的成員名單，只交代有港台助理廣播處長張健華，以及來自行政主任、庫務會計師和管理參議主任等職系的現職公務員等人，從未公開全部成員的姓名。</span><br />\n<br />\n記者昨日要求公開成員名單，商經局常任秘書長梁卓文避而不答，僅指小組其他成員包括行政主任、具管理和採購經驗人士等。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：AO空降接管 梁家榮提前解約<br />\n<br />\n丁葉燕薇為首長級政務主任，2009年擔任。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"ff9eb1a1c4f03493a8fd2e12ba8a90ebe4494d14","tid":2415443,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T08:59:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭心腹？似佢阿妹多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e06a35203473918d0c1caa0a7ab71d227581653","tid":2415443,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34928e79e44b6df4cb1a7d7db72adc625ea22ce3","tid":2415443,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e06a35203473918d0c1caa0a7ab71d227581653","tid":2415443,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:04:45.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，林奠嚟嘅喂"},{"pid":"de925629e29c68e1702db59a25bd94bd22a8e92d","tid":2415443,"uid":282347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e06a35203473918d0c1caa0a7ab71d227581653","tid":2415443,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭改圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"蜥蜴人嘅outfit嚟，要幾多有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0f0d8715017c49b7bfef2ed1948ebaa46ffe88","tid":2415443,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:11:57.000Z","msg":"問責意識最薄弱既政府高層批評人地問責意識薄弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b506fe69537622e2883d2c89a0d5dde45a5922e","tid":2415443,"uid":304916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"林奠心腹定分身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}